package com.finals.friendsfinder.views.home.data

data class PrivacyPolicyModel(
    val policy: String = "Welcome to Friends Finder. We are committed to protecting your personal information and building a safe and trustworthy environment for all users. This privacy policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use the Friends Finder app. By using the Friends Finder app, you agree to the collection and use of your information under the terms below.\n" +
            "1. Collection of Personal Information: When you use Friends Finder, we may collect your personal information, including your location, to improve the user experience and provide the best service for you. Location information will be used to display a list of friends or users you may be interested in around you.\n" +
            "2. Use of Personal Information: We will use your personal information to provide services such as finding friends, suggesting new friends, or providing location information. We may also use this information to improve and optimize the user experience on the app.\n" +
            "3. Protection of Personal Information: We are committed to protecting your personal information and using appropriate security measures to prevent unauthorized access, loss of data, or misuse. We will not share your personal information with any third party without your consent.\n" +
            "4. Privacy Settings Adjustment: You can adjust your privacy settings in the Friends Finder app settings. This way, you can decide whether you want to share your location and with whom.\n" +
            "5. Policy Changes: We may update this privacy policy over time without prior notice. You should check regularly to understand the latest changes.\n" +
            "Contact:\n" +
            "If you have any questions or requests regarding our privacy policy, please contact us via email: privacy@friendsfinder.com.\n" +
            "By using the Friends Finder app, you accept and agree to this privacy policy. We value your trust and are committed to protecting your personal information to the best of our ability.\n"
)
